metadata.name: MONEY
metadata.description:
nail designs, especially on exaggerated and long nail lengths, is a staple in black self-expression that has been labeled as “ghetto”, “loud”, “unprofessional” - but we should recognize it for what it truly is - an art form. this collection features original nail designs, handmade by me, then photographed to emphasize and appreciate the fine details and artistry that goes into each design.

money - genuine $1 USD bill formed into french tips formed on the nail, adorned with hand-placed gold and silver chain accents.
